# ========================================
# ABYSS-MONOREPO — ROOT .gitignore
# Generated: 2026-04-15 · Audit: 2026-04-15-audit-clearance
# Owner: Dr. Ferdi Iskandar (drClassy)
# ========================================
#
# GOLDEN RULE: core `.agent/` governance docs (HANDOFF, CONTEXT, DECISIONS,
#              PROGRESS, README), `CLAUDE.md`, `pnpm-lock.yaml`, shared `.cursor/`
#              project config, `.cursorignore`, and `mcp.json.example` are
#              TRACKED BY DESIGN. apps/ and packages/sentra/ are excluded
#              (private/proprietary). Operational agent logs, archive, hooks,
#              scripts, and local planning artifacts stay LOCAL ONLY.
#              Local-only: `.mcp.json`, `.claude/`, `.agent/archive/`,
#              `.agent/hooks/`, `.agent/sessions/`, `.agent/reports/`,
#              `docs/superpowers/`, `.roomodes`.
# ========================================

# ---- SECRETS & ENV (NEVER COMMIT) ----
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.*.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.cert
*.crt
secrets.json
secrets.yaml
secrets.yml
credentials.json
